node.text:
Circuit breaker day 44: Missing my breakfast of economical fried bee hoon.

Decided to make one with whatever I can find in the fridge. 👩‍🍳 Stir fried silver needle noodles (a.k.a mee tai mak) with cabbage and topped with a sunny side up. This shall be it. 🥰

Happy Mid Week! 🤗
#sgunited #circuitbreaker #stayhomesg
